</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        habt, ewch wissen ze lassen als von <add><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan></add>
                        des <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>durlewchtigst<ex>en</ex></expan> fürsten und
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Sig<ex>mund,</ex></expan>
<expan>römisch<ex>em</ex></expan> und zu <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc.
                        kunigs, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedigst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        wol ver<expan>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> und tun <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> ze wissen, daz
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> der römisch künig, auf heint gen
                                <expan>Halsprunn<ex>en</ex></expan> und auf morn her gen
                                <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> sol. Und reiten mit im unser
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> der <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
                        von <expan>Sachs<ex>en</ex></expan> und burggraf
                            <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Nür<ex>emberg,</ex></expan>
                        so hat er <expan>ettlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürst<ex>en,</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> und <expan>stett<ex>en</ex></expan> nemlich
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan>
<add>den bischofen</add> von <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g,</expan> von
                                <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, von Eystett,
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Johans<ex>en</ex></expan> von Peyern, burggraf
                                <expan>Johans<ex>en</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, und <expan>etliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu im her gen
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>küntt</expan> ze <expan>kome<ex>n,</ex></expan>
<add>den auch herberg bey uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>fangen</expan> ist. Auch
                                    <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                    <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz unsers
                                    <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, des künigs von Beheim, ret zu im
                            her gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>, und ist uns gesagt, daz er als von
                        eins <expan>gemeine<ex>n</ex></expan> frids <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        maine zureden; ob dem also sey <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> wie sich das
                        machen <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, wissen wir noch niht
                                <expan>aigensch<ex>aft</ex></expan>. Denn
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>es</expan>, daz wir iht treffenlichs erfüren
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> gewar <expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        daz uns <expan>notdurft<ex>en</ex></expan> dewht,
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ze
                        <expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan>, das <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                        bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> selbs <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun. Wan wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
